      "content": "but i dont really want to deal with the wait at urgent care and it's so expensive. i honestly doubt it's broken, it just feels like a really bad strain. can't i just take some ibuprofen and keep it iced for like 48 hours to see if the swelling goes down? i feel like i can manage it at home if i just stay off it.",
