    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what u mean about the red flags but i've had bad sprains before and they always feel like this. i just really need to know for sure—if i do the RICE method strictly for the next two days and the swelling starts going down, is it safe to assume it's just a sprain and i don't need that x-ray? i just want a way to handle this myself so i don't waste money on a doctor if i don't have to.",
